skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dog quotes
des: An entertainment skill in which some of the most recognizable quotes are imagined through the voice of a dog. To use, say alexa open dog quotes. After getting a dog quote say tell me a dog quote, or tell me another, to get another dog quote. When you are done using Dog Quotes say stop, quit or close. For help say 'alexa ask dog quotes for help."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
